title: Diamond Beat
sinopse:
She was born into a family of classical musicians, but Satsuki is the one drop out. She thought that she hated music; but, then, a prince with a guitar appears?! "You are a genius DIVA!" That’s a lie, right—?!

(Source: Midnight Scans)

Included one-shots: Yuki, Doki, Suki, 7 Days Cinderella
